  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02964', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於煙囪效應之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["當室內溫度愈高，煙囪效應之中性帶向上偏移", "上部開口越大，煙囪效應之中性帶會上移", "火災發生在中性帶以下之樓層，煙會隨著煙囪效應迅速由垂直通道向上竄升", "火災發生於中性帶以上之樓層，則煙將由建築物該層之開口直接排出起火樓層外"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b33459e35331", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45db166de921", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02965', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種物質狀態最有利於燃燒？', '["發熱量低且熱傳導度高", "發熱量高且熱傳導度高", "發熱量高且熱傳導度低", "發熱量低且熱傳導度低"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b33459e35331", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45db166de921", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
